item.title: glimpses Insights
item.description: Thought of sharing the video that shows my humble effort to create simple interactive visualizaton of the global distribution of glimpses users with maximum sessions. Thanks to Tableau Public and github-pages with which I could do this. Tableau Public is a free software that can connect to a file or a server and create stunning interactive data visualizations for the web. Please be aware that as the name suggests Tableau public is 100% public and not recommended to sharing private or proprietary data.
